steps.name: Click on Maintenance and click Procedures
"Find Procedure" window is open and click Add button
"Add Procedure" window is opened and enter Procedure Name
Click ellipsis button next to the Data Sheet "Attach Data Sheet" window is open
Select "Procedure" for the "Search Value" and click Find button
Click ellipsis button next to Category (proc) "Select Category (Proc)" window is open
Select specific "MET/CAL" from the grid and click OK button
Click Save button and click Close button
